---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy | SUDATA">
	<div class="flex flex-col w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-24 sm:pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-16 sm:pb-20 md:pb-24 px-4 space-y-10">

		<header class="space-y-2">
			<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-sudata-neon tracking-widest neon-text-shadow font-mono-tech">
				Privacy
			</h1>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey/50 font-mono-tech text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
				Last updated April 2026
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Who we are</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				SUDATA (Sydney University Data Society) is a student-run club at the University of Sydney.
				This website is maintained by the SUDATA technical team and is used to share information
				about events, sponsors, and career opportunities.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">What we collect</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				If you accept the cookie banner, we store an anonymous random ID in a cookie named
				<span class="text-sudata-cyan font-mono-tech">_vid</span> that persists for 12 months.
				This ID has no connection to your name, email address, or any other personal information.
			</p>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				Using this ID we record:
			</p>
			<ul class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-sudata-neon/20">
				<li>Which pages you visited</li>
				<li>Which links you clicked (e.g. sponsor websites, event signups)</li>
				<li>The page you came from (referrer)</li>
				<li>The approximate time of each visit</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				If you decline, we use a temporary session ID instead that resets when you close the tab.
				The same visit data is still recorded, but you cannot be recognised across separate visits.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">What we do not collect</h2>
			<ul class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-sudata-neon/20">
				<li>No name, email address, or login credentials</li>
				<li>No payment or financial information</li>
				<li>No IP address stored in our database</li>
				<li>No data shared with or sold to third parties</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Why we collect it</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				Analytics data helps the SUDATA exec team understand which pages and content are most
				useful to visitors — for example, which sponsor opportunities or events get the most
				engagement. This informs how we structure the site and what we report to sponsors.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Data retention</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				The <span class="text-sudata-cyan">_vid</span> cookie expires after 12 months.
				Analytics records in our database are kept for up to 12 months and then deleted.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Your choices</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				You can decline the cookie banner on your first visit. You can also change your mind at
				any time by clearing your browser cookies and localStorage, which will reset the banner
				on your next visit.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-3">
			<h2 class="text-sudata-neon/80 font-mono-tech text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Contact</h2>
			<p class="text-sudata-grey font-mono-tech text-sm leading-relaxed">
				Questions about this policy can be directed to the SUDATA technical team at
				<a href="mailto:technology@sudata.org" class="text-sudata-cyan hover:underline underline-offset-2">
					technology@sudata.org
				</a>.
			</p>
		</section>

	</div>
</Layout>
